    {
      "id": "AJSr9S74HLsT7oOmcjsCb",
      "questionNumber": 8,
      "questionText": "To get an output of 1 from the circuit shown in figure the input must be :\n<br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l82xl7r1/a3efb46a-e95d-4c84-9a30-09cfa4d28ab2/4587a9e0-34e4-11ed-b84c-a3c7c2456516/file-1l82xl7r2.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l82xl7r1/a3efb46a-e95d-4c84-9a30-09cfa4d28ab2/4587a9e0-34e4-11ed-b84c-a3c7c2456516/file-1l82xl7r2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2016 (Online) 10th April Morning Slot Physics - Semiconductor Question 196 English\">",
